detailed_guest_info: The podcast guest is Bellinzona, a historic Swiss town and the capital of the canton of Ticino in Switzerland. It is known for its three castles, Castelgrande, Montebello, and Sasso Corbaro, which are UNESCO World Heritage Sites. Bellinzona is situated east of the river Ticino, nestled at the foot of the Alps, and is surrounded by the Lepontine Alps and Lugano Prealps.

podcast_details.author: Ten Minute Podcast
podcast_details.summary: A podcast formerly hosted by Will Sasso (MADtv, The Three Stooges, lots of other stuff) that featured he and his funny pals doing lots of super fun bits, jumping into some silly characters and impersonations, and ruthlessly belittling one another for real the way only good friends can. Ten Minute Podcast is recess for adults. Pass it on!

podcast_summary:
- TL;DR: Comedians Will Sasso and Chad Kultgen have launched a new podcast called Dudezy, available on YouTube and podcast platforms.
- Bullet Point 1: The podcast is run entirely by a first-of-its-kind artificial intelligence, making each episode better than the last.
- Bullet Point 2: It has similarities and DNA from their previous podcast, the 10 Minute Podcast, with familiar elements for fans.
- Bullet Point 3: Dudezy releases new episodes every Tuesday, offering a blend of comedy and impersonations.
- Surprising Fact: The podcast's unique approach of using AI to improve episodes sets it apart from other podcasts.
- Inspiring Takeaway: Sasso and Kultgen invite listeners to join them on this new venture, emphasizing the importance of their friends-turned-listeners.
